Fresh off the red carpet this past week!

One of the most rewarding projects I’ve been apart of as an actor thus far is getting the chance to work with the incomparable @i_believebynadia. In addition to her absolute heart of gold, she is one crazy talented actress, writer, and director. “I Loved You More” is her first ever feature (the first of MANY) and from the moment we met each other to rehearse two years ago, discussing the character development of “Lauren” and “Tyrone”, it was an instant click of creative collaboration / connection as artists and human beings. Not many know how vulnerable and BRAVE you have to be to share your story and make it into a dang feature film for the masses to watch! Nadi WORKS! I always told her, ‘put out the art and watch the blessings fall.’ Now look at God working. She’s INCREDIBLE. 🙌🏽🙏🏽

To be a star amongst stars such as Nadi, @bigmamalina , @crystal.the.doll , @kamalsmith2 , @spankdabank__ and so many more has been nothing short of a blessing from God and I’m beyond grateful to all of you. 

Nadi has already announced ILYM2 sooo…see y’all back on set soon! Time to get back to work!lol 🙌🏽🎬🎥 .

Every once-in-a-while my job as a journalist meets my world as an actor. lol 
.
Where are all of my @snowfallfx fans at!? I got the opportunity to interview the incomparable Queen, AND DETROIT’S OWN, @luvangelalewis AKA ‘Aunt Louie’ for #CurrentSports! We talked about how she landed the role of Louie via self-tape, the importance of understanding the selective VALUE that an actor must weigh when deciding on a role, the impact of the late John Singleton, being from ‘The D’, and SO MUCH MORE! She was / is incredible. 
.
Interview dropping Monday.

🚨NEW FILM ALERT - ‘LOOM - The Found Footage Horror Short’ a film by Jason Gaines - LINK IN BIO 🎬
.
When I first got the call from my brotha T-Rich about a possible horror short, I was excited to FINALLY collab with a talent like him. I then spoke to the mastermind that is Jason and he began to pitch to me the idea and his vision for ‘Byron’. I knew that this would challenge me in a way that I haven’t been challenged as an actor before. There’s nothing better than a challenge as an artist. I was IN. 
.
Being such a major fan of the horror genre, I was so anxious to be able to dive into it and play a bit! Being surrounded by the talents that are T-Rich, JG, and Britt made it SEAMLESS.
.
Watch. Enjoy. Comment. Like. Share! Blessings.

A small peak in to my weekly process and habitude as an actor. I take the same approach to acting that I did / do in my athletic world. It’s about practice. Daily repetition. Trying new things. Seeing what works. Seeing what doesn’t work. Practice. Practice. PRACTICE. Over and over and over and over. Obsession. Until I feel like I’ve gotten as close to humanly possible to a human-concentrate experience on camera. Be obsessive. Do the work. The work of an artist. 
.
.
.
.

🚨 NEW HORROR FILM ALERT🚨 LINK IN BIO
.
From the mind and lens of my brotha @lonevisionary , please watch and share the horror 💀👻🎃 short film 🎬 “Alone”!!!
.
.
Jason and I shot this joint back in June. Just him and I on set…throwing ideas at the wall…exploring different possibilities between “action” and “cut”…trying new things…listening to each other…trial and error…this works…this doesn’t…how about we do it this way?…can we do that?…let’s change this…tweak that…I’m talking about one of the dopest collaborative experiences I’ve had on set, while also motivating one another and having candid discussions about dreams and goals. 
.
.
My brotha, thanks for allowing me to explore as an actor and trusting me with your amazing material. There is no limit on your extraordinary work. Beyond blessed to be apart of it. Let us know what you think, good ppl! 🙏🏽

“Alone” is here! From the mind of @lonevisionary , I had so much fun making Sam and his various layers come alive. The perfect #Halloween season horror short! 

See why Sam is so troubled. Have you ever felt…alone? 🤔🎃🎬 

Watch. Like. Share! Link in bio!

#horror #horrormovies #halloween #halloweenmovie #horrorfan #horrormovie #horroraddict

🚨 YES, ANOTHER NEW HORROR SHORT FILM 🚨- “Calling Hours” by @bemvp.co - LINK IN BIO
.
.
When my brotha @trichofficial recommended me for this horror short film role, I didn’t know how much of a blessing it would become. I got the script from the great Jon Phou...heard his pitch / concept idea for this wonderful piece of work…it would be a film competing in the @horrorfilmroulette challenge (shout-out to Erik Steele and Josh Taube!) and was so unique and well thought out that I jumped at the opportunity. It presented no written dialogue, meaning the selling point as a performer would be grounded in physical expression. The challenge yielded this result. A result that we all are incredibly proud of. Shot in one day. 12 straight hours.
.
.
A special thanks to the remarkable team over at @bemvp.co …they blew everyone away. The vision from Jon and Nick @hustleberryfin was such a pleasure to be apart of and they even took home the ‘Best Cinematography’ award. Beyond talented. And can’t forget about Austin as well @amf.1235 who made sure our audio was on point and constantly checked on us actors. Also, to my co-star Gabrielle Bryson…such a pleasure sharing the screen with you. These two roles required vulnerability and you were a remarkable scene partner. 
.
.
Enjoy…and, what do you think happened? Any guesses? Let the debate begin and STILL Happy Halloween! 
.
.
#Halloween #HorrorFilms #Horror #HorrorMovie#Acting #Actor #Film

It has always been a dream to rock-out a golf ⛳️ commercial as an actor, seeing as though the sport has become my number one hobby. I had the amazing opportunity to do just that, working with the phenomenal team at @thequirkcreative for this @mizuho.americas spot starring the golfing LEGEND @michellewiewest. We knocked this out in just six hours at @libertynationalgc, right before the @mizuholpga was scheduled to start. Mind-blowing. 
.
.
A special thanks goes to @justconfess and @c._.watts who trusted me with the part and had such a dope vision for the piece! @natyloff who helped keep everything running so smoothly and was a star. And then there’s the newly found homies-fo-life in my bruh @rashadtaylormua (000000666!!! 🤙🏽) and the graceful queen that is @wardrobebreakdown who had a brotha looking like straight money. lol! All REMARKABLY talented individuals who make working in this business a joy. And Michelle was, as expected, a natural! Class personified and it was an honor to work with her. She even gave Al Woods some tips on his swing. 🏌🏽lol! An honor to play her caddie lol
.
And a BIG UPS to the best reps in the biz. @maultsby_talent_agency , I’m so grateful for you. Sooo grateful. 
.
.
.
Blessings on blessings. 🙏🏽
.

That’s right beautiful ppl…I’ve got a sports magazine special coming your way that ANYONE will enjoy. One of the stories highlighted is the pickleball boom, which seems to be growing by the day. Tune in to see what the hype is all about on ‘Beyond the Score’ — Thu, Dec 14 at 8:30pm ET on WKAR TV AND YouTube LIVE (WKAR). Mark your calendars! 
.
.
.
Much thanks to my incredible senior producer @superyanchoandsqaz and the PHENOMENAL team at @5thmediallc — the brothas @genewilsonv and @cmo_the_artist have done some SPECIAL with this. I’m beyond blessed to work with such talented people.

🚨”BEYOND THE SCORE WITH AL MARTIN”PREMIERES THURSDAY AT 8:30PM! WATCH ON WKARTV OR WKAR’S YOUTUBE PAGE! 🚨 

Al Martin uncovers stories where sports and society intersect.

In this WKAR special: taking a knee during the national anthem results in a transformative journey for a star Lansing-area quarterback; a boxing coach creates an adaptive job-sharing program; and the popularity of pickleball surges thanks to its cross-generational appeal.

📺

What more can I say about these amazing people? The TRUE stars of ‘Beyond the Score’. 
.
Number 1…God gets all the glory. It is through Him that I’m able to do what I love in my careers of acting and broadcasting and He will always get the glory. 
.
This wouldn’t have happened if it wasn’t for our fearless leader...WKAR General Manager Shawn Turner...trusting me with this project. Coming to me about the idea to sunset Current Sports after a decade of programming so that I could focus on creating a new sports television show…one that I’ve always wanted to do... drawing from the inspiration of some of my favs like ESPN’s 30 for 30, Vice News, and, MY TOP show, HBO’s Real Sports. 
.
My senior producer Carol Yancho is is an absolute godsend. WOW. WOW. WOW. I mean, she was always there…always helping plan…coordinate…guide…ENCOURAGE. Like I told her, we were a Jordan-Pippen duo in this thing. I could not have done this without her and she is one of the most talented, driven, and caring people I’ve ever met in my life. I can’t thank-you enough and your light shines all throughout this special. 
.
Carlos and Gene…my brothas. I knew that I wanted this show to have a different look / feel in comparison your ordinary local sports TV show. I also felt strongly that THEY were the ones that could not only pull this off, but do it exceptionally well. Expanding our creative partnership from film to the field of broadcast with BTS became one of the biggest blessings in my life and watching them work inspires the heck out of me. It always does. With BTS I wanted grounded, journalistic storytelling,...but with a cinematic look. These two are bonafide genius’ and I’m sure you can see that through each and every frame. Words can’t express truly how thankful I am to you both. 
.
Nathan, Drew, Casey, Elena, Jason, Dan, Brant, Melanie, Kate, Bill, Jordan, Johnny… and so many more!
.
I am merely the front porch of this show…they are the foundation holding it all together. 
. 
Enjoy tonight’s premiere, ladies and gents. Much love and blessings. - AL

Merry Christmas! 🎄

While you’re partaking in the holiday festivities with the fam, take a break to check out the latest collaboration with my brothas @lonevisionary and @ilovejaysquared ! Link is in the bio. 

Working with them has become such a creative blessing! Family, no doubt. 

So, yes...we made CHRISTMAS HORROR SHORT 🎄🎅🏽! “Christmas Cravings” — ‘Leaving 🥛milk and cookies 🍪 out becomes an ominous offering to a mysterious supernatural entity.’ Also, @angiespfx CRUSHED IT! 

Can’t wait for you to check it out and tell us what you think. It was fun playing Jake. MERRY CHRISTMAS, YA FILTHY ANIMALS!

2023…the year of relentless work. 🎬 Glory to God.
.
.
From #Loom to #Alone to #CallingHours to #ChristmasCravings ...to putting a bow on #GrandRiver to #Cultivar to #DZ48 to #AllThatRemains to #GoldOnes to #GrimleysGamble …to commercial work for #Hoodz to #Mizho to #DBZ to #ABCNYC to #MSUFCU …to a new sports TV show special #BeyondTheScore… I have pushed myself creatively / professionally this year more than any other year and I’m STILL just getting started. Grateful to God for a creative family that constantly inspires me and I can’t wait to reach out to you all. 
.
.
2024…it’s time to push things to another level. Hungry is an understatement. I’m blessed beyond measure and so ready for what’s to come. Much love, good ppl.

Watch “Christmas Cravings” 🎄🎅🏽 now! From the 🧠 of the great @lonevisionary !! 🎬🎥
